==Minimum age of marriage== The personal status code sets the minimum age of marriage at 18 years. However, since consensual sex outside of marriage is illegal, a legal guardian can ask local authorities to permit a girl younger than 18 to marry.<ref name="girlsnotbrides.org"/>
